Enhancing your feminine charm and making you look simple yet stunningly beautiful is this classy creation from the house of Caprese. This large-sized tote bag is made of faux leather and hence ensures secure and sturdy support to all the essentials you require during your outdoor jaunts. Equipped with five pockets this satchel comes with the capacity to accommodate pretty much everything you stash while use. You could also settle your nitty-gritties in an orderly manner in the roomy interiors of this Caprese Cara Tote – For Women. Additionally the zippered closure in this bag safely encases your essentials within.

The elegant buckle detailing on the flap of the front pocket certainly enhances the smart look of this tote bag. With the drop handle measuring 228.6 mm you can be ensured of simple effortless and hassle-free portability while you are on the move. Besides this the Caprese Cara Tote – For Women is also equipped with slip pockets and zippered pockets hence adding to the convenience while use. Furthermore this tote bag comes with a Jacquard Lining and a Nickel Finish Neo Detailing. Measuring 430 x 445 x 90 mm in dimension this casual Caprese Cara Tote – For Women is lightweight and is easy to haul along.
